item.title: Những chữ đầu tiên
item.description: Hi! This is for Hieu in the future. Very nice working on your first web! I am proud of you, please don’t be skeptical of yourself, even though I bet that you are right now haha. Anyhow, if you feel so, remember that everything is going to be daijoubu.
